WEBVTT

00:03.687 --> 00:05.290
Everybody has feelings.

00:06.648 --> 00:07.863
Kids have feelings.

00:08.013 --> 00:09.496
Adults have feelings.

00:10.180 --> 00:11.733
And even pets do.

00:12.362 --> 00:16.097
Sad, happy, excited, joyful.

00:16.375 --> 00:21.872
It's important that you don't get exciting and happy mixed up.

00:22.267 --> 00:27.465
Sometimes you feel sad but you're not going to feel sad forever.

00:27.699 --> 00:31.446
If you're feeling sad, you can change.

00:31.585 --> 00:39.815
If you do the pause button, you can pause and just rethink that moment.

00:40.579 --> 00:43.884
You can think of other people's feelings.

00:44.126 --> 00:49.669
If someone was sad and you really wanted to help them,...

00:51.085 --> 00:56.815
...you can think about how they're feeling right now and how you can help them.

00:57.549 --> 00:59.930
Everybody has feelings.

01:00.125 --> 01:02.276
Just sometimes your feelings change.

